51  /// BellElementShape
52  ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
53  ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
54 
55  //========================================================================
56  /// A class for Bell triangular shape function with 3 vertex nodes and
57  /// WITHOUT 3 middle-side node
58  //========================================================================
59  template<unsigned DIM>
60  class BellElementShape
61  {
62  };
63 
64  template<>
65  class BellElementShape<2>
66  {
67  public:
68  //=======================================================================
69  /// Return local coordinates of node j
70  //=======================================================================
71  void local_coordinate_of_node(const unsigned& j, Vector<double>& s) const
72  {
73  switch (j)
74  {
75  case 0:
76  s[0] = 1.0;
77  s[1] = 0.0;
78  break;
79 
80  case 1:
81  s[0] = 0.0;
82  s[1] = 1.0;
83  break;
84 
85  case 2:
86  s[0] = 0.0;
87  s[1] = 0.0;
88  break;
89 
90  default:
91  std::ostringstream error_message;
92  error_message
93  << "Element only has three nodes; called with node number " << j
94  << std::endl;
95 
96  throw OomphLibError(error_message.str(),
97  "BellElement::local_coordinate_of_node()",
98  OOMPH_EXCEPTION_LOCATION);
99  }
100  }
101 
102  void Bshape(const Vector<double>& s,
103  Shape& psi,
104  DenseMatrix<double>& position) const
105  {
106  //---------------------------------------------
107  // the mapping to physical coordinates
108  //----------------------------------------------
109  Vector<double> phi(2);
110  phi[0] = position(2, 0) + (position(0, 0) - position(2, 0)) * s[0] +
111  (position(1, 0) - position(2, 0)) * s[1];
112  phi[1] = position(2, 1) + (position(0, 1) - position(2, 1)) * s[0] +
113  (position(1, 1) - position(2, 1)) * s[1];
114 
115  double A =
116  ((position(1, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(1, 1)) -
117  (position(0, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(0, 1)) +
118  (position(0, 0) * position(1, 1) - position(1, 0) * position(0, 1))) /
119  2.0;
120  double A0 =
121  ((position(1, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(1, 1)) -
122  (phi[0] * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * phi[1]) +
123  (phi[0] * position(1, 1) - position(1, 0) * phi[1])) /
124  2.0;
125  double A1 =
126  ((phi[0] * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * phi[1]) -
127  (position(0, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(0, 1)) +
128  (position(0, 0) * phi[1] - phi[0] * position(0, 1))) /
129  2.0;
130  double A2 =
131  ((position(1, 0) * phi[1] - phi[0] * position(1, 1)) -
132  (position(0, 0) * phi[1] - phi[0] * position(0, 1)) +
133  (position(0, 0) * position(1, 1) - position(1, 0) * position(0, 1))) /
134  2.0;
135  // assigned area coordinates
136  Vector<double> xi(3);
137  xi[0] = A0 / A;
138  xi[1] = A1 / A;
139  xi[2] = A2 / A;
140 
141  Vector<double> b(3);
142  Vector<double> c(3);
143  Vector<double> lamb(3);
144  Vector<double> lamb_p(3);
145  Vector<double> pp(2);
146  Vector<double> a(2), cc(2);
147 
148  // compute for b and c
149  b[1] = position(0, 0) - position(2, 0);
150  b[2] = position(1, 0) - position(0, 0);
151  b[0] = position(2, 0) - position(1, 0);
152 
153  c[1] = position(2, 1) - position(0, 1);
154  c[2] = position(0, 1) - position(1, 1);
155  c[0] = position(1, 1) - position(2, 1);
156 
157  // compute for a point of perpendicular
158  // on the edge opposite to node0 (top vertex)
159  Vector<double> v(2);
160  v[0] = (position(2, 0) - position(1, 0));
161  v[1] = (position(2, 1) - position(1, 1));
162  double m = v[1] / v[0];
163  a[0] = position(1, 0);
164  a[1] = position(1, 1);
165  cc[0] = position(0, 0);
166  cc[1] = position(0, 1);
167  if (v[0] == 0)
168  {
169  m = v[0] / v[1];
170  pp[1] = (v[0] * m * a[1] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[0] * a[0] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
171  ((v[0] * m) + v[1]);
172  pp[0] = (pp[1] - a[1]) * m + a[0];
173  }
174  else
175  {
176  pp[0] = (v[1] * m * a[0] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[1] * a[1] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
177  (v[1] * m + v[0]);
178  pp[1] = m * (pp[0] - a[0]) + a[1];
179  }
180  double l = sqrt(v[0] * v[0] + v[1] * v[1]);
181  double l1 =
182  sqrt((pp[0] - a[0]) * (pp[0] - a[0]) + (pp[1] - a[1]) * (pp[1] - a[1]));
183  lamb_p[0] = l1 / l;
184  lamb[0] = 1 - lamb_p[0];
185 
186  // on the edge opposite to node1
187  v[0] = (position(0, 0) - position(2, 0));
188  v[1] = (position(0, 1) - position(2, 1));
189  m = v[1] / v[0];
190  a[0] = position(2, 0);
191  a[1] = position(2, 1);
192  cc[0] = position(1, 0);
193  cc[1] = position(1, 1);
194  if (v[0] == 0)
195  {
196  m = v[0] / v[1];
197  pp[1] = (v[0] * m * a[1] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[0] * a[0] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
198  ((v[0] * m) + v[1]);
199  pp[0] = (pp[1] - a[1]) * m + a[0];
200  }
201  else
202  {
203  pp[0] = (v[1] * m * a[0] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[1] * a[1] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
204  (v[1] * m + v[0]);
205  pp[1] = m * (pp[0] - a[0]) + a[1];
206  }
207  l = sqrt(v[0] * v[0] + v[1] * v[1]);
208  l1 =
209  sqrt((pp[0] - a[0]) * (pp[0] - a[0]) + (pp[1] - a[1]) * (pp[1] - a[1]));
210  lamb_p[1] = l1 / l;
211  lamb[1] = 1 - lamb_p[1];
212 
213  // on the edge opposite to node2 (right bottom)
214  v[0] = (position(1, 0) - position(0, 0));
215  v[1] = (position(1, 1) - position(0, 1));
216  m = v[1] / v[0];
217  a[0] = position(0, 0);
218  a[1] = position(0, 1);
219  cc[0] = position(2, 0);
220  cc[1] = position(2, 1);
221  if (v[0] == 0)
222  {
223  m = v[0] / v[1];
224  pp[1] = (v[0] * m * a[1] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[0] * a[0] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
225  ((v[0] * m) + v[1]);
226  pp[0] = (pp[1] - a[1]) * m + a[0];
227  }
228  else
229  {
230  pp[0] = (v[1] * m * a[0] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[1] * a[1] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
231  (v[1] * m + v[0]);
232  pp[1] = m * (pp[0] - a[0]) + a[1];
233  }
234  l = sqrt(v[0] * v[0] + v[1] * v[1]);
235  l1 =
236  sqrt((pp[0] - a[0]) * (pp[0] - a[0]) + (pp[1] - a[1]) * (pp[1] - a[1]));
237  lamb_p[2] = l1 / l;
238  lamb[2] = 1 - lamb_p[2];
239 
240  // define shape functions that associated to dofs at node 0
241  psi(0, 0) =
242  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] +
243  5.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (xi[1] + xi[2]) +
244  10.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (xi[1] + xi[2]) * (xi[1] + xi[2]) +
245  30.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
246  (lamb[2] * xi[1] + lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
247  psi(0, 1) = 3.0 * b[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[1] - xi[2]) +
248  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (b[2] * xi[1] - b[1] * xi[2]) *
249  (xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1] + 4 * xi[2]) +
250  15 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
251  (b[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] - b[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
252  psi(0, 2) =
253  -3.0 * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[1] - xi[2]) -
254  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (c[2] * xi[1] - c[1] * xi[2]) *
255  (xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2]) -
256  15.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
257  (c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] - c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
258  psi(0, 3) =
259  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] *
260  (b[2] * b[2] * xi[1] * xi[1] + b[1] * b[1] * xi[2] * xi[2]) +
261  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
262  (-b[1] * b[2] * xi[0] + b[2] * b[0] * xi[1] + b[0] * b[1] * xi[2]) +
263  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
264  (b[2] * b[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] + b[1] * b[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
265  psi(0, 4) =
266  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] *
267  (c[2] * c[2] * xi[1] * xi[1] + c[1] * c[1] * xi[2] * xi[2]) +
268  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
269  (-c[1] * c[2] * xi[0] + c[2] * c[0] * xi[1] + c[0] * c[1] * xi[2]) +
270  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
271  (c[2] * c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] + c[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
272  psi(0, 5) =
273  b[0] * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[0] + xi[1] + xi[2]) +
274  b[1] * c[1] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] *
275  (xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[1]) +
276  b[2] * c[2] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
277  (xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[2] * xi[2]) -
278  5.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
279  (b[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2] + b[2] * c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1]);
280 
281  // define shape functions that associated to dofs at node 1
282  psi(1, 0) =
283  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] +
284  5.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (xi[2] + xi[0]) +
285  10.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (xi[2] + xi[0]) * (xi[2] + xi[0]) +
286  30.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
287  (lamb[0] * xi[2] + lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
288  psi(1, 1) = 3.0 * b[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[2] - xi[0]) +
289  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (b[0] * xi[2] - b[2] * xi[0]) *
290  (xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2] + 4 * xi[0]) +
291  15 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
292  (b[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] - b[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
293  psi(1, 2) =
294  -3.0 * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[2] - xi[0]) -
295  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (c[0] * xi[2] - c[2] * xi[0]) *
296  (xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0]) -
297  15.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
298  (c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] - c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
299  psi(1, 3) =
300  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] *
301  (b[0] * b[0] * xi[2] * xi[2] + b[2] * b[2] * xi[0] * xi[0]) +
302  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
303  (-b[2] * b[0] * xi[1] + b[0] * b[1] * xi[2] + b[1] * b[2] * xi[0]) +
304  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
305  (b[0] * b[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] + b[2] * b[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
306  psi(1, 4) =
307  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] *
308  (c[0] * c[0] * xi[2] * xi[2] + c[2] * c[2] * xi[0] * xi[0]) +
309  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
310  (-c[2] * c[0] * xi[1] + c[0] * c[1] * xi[2] + c[1] * c[2] * xi[0]) +
311  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
312  (c[0] * c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] + c[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
313  psi(1, 5) =
314  b[1] * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[1] + xi[2] + xi[0]) +
315  b[2] * c[2] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] *
316  (xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[2]) +
317  b[0] * c[0] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
318  (xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[0] * xi[0]) -
319  5.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
320  (b[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0] + b[0] * c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2]);
321 
322  // define shape functions that associated to dofs at node 2
323  psi(2, 0) =
324  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] +
325  5.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (xi[0] + xi[1]) +
326  10.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (xi[0] + xi[1]) * (xi[0] + xi[1]) +
327  30.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
328  (lamb[1] * xi[0] + lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
329  psi(2, 1) = 3.0 * b[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[0] - xi[1]) +
330  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (b[1] * xi[0] - b[0] * xi[1]) *
331  (xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0] + 4 * xi[1]) +
332  15 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
333  (b[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] - b[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
334  psi(2, 2) =
335  -3.0 * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[0] - xi[1]) -
336  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (c[1] * xi[0] - c[0] * xi[1]) *
337  (xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1]) -
338  15.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
339  (c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] - c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
340  psi(2, 3) =
341  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] *
342  (b[1] * b[1] * xi[0] * xi[0] + b[0] * b[0] * xi[1] * xi[1]) +
343  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
344  (-b[0] * b[1] * xi[2] + b[1] * b[2] * xi[0] + b[2] * b[0] * xi[1]) +
345  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
346  (b[1] * b[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] + b[0] * b[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
347  psi(2, 4) =
348  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] *
349  (c[1] * c[1] * xi[0] * xi[0] + c[0] * c[0] * xi[1] * xi[1]) +
350  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
351  (-c[0] * c[1] * xi[2] + c[1] * c[2] * xi[0] + c[2] * c[0] * xi[1]) +
352  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
353  (c[1] * c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] + c[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
354  psi(2, 5) =
355  b[2] * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[2] + xi[0] + xi[1]) +
356  b[0] * c[0] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] *
357  (xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[0]) +
358  b[1] * c[1] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
359  (xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[1] * xi[1]) -
360  5.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
361  (b[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1] + b[1] * c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0]);
362  }
363 
364  void dBshape_local(const Vector<double>& s,
365  Shape& psi,
366  DShape& dpsids,
367  DenseMatrix<double>& position) const
368  {
369  // assign for shape functions
370  Bshape(s, psi, position);
371  //---------------------------------------------
372  // the mapping to physical coordinates
373  //----------------------------------------------
374  Vector<double> phi(2);
375  phi[0] = position(2, 0) + (position(0, 0) - position(2, 0)) * s[0] +
376  (position(1, 0) - position(2, 0)) * s[1];
377  phi[1] = position(2, 1) + (position(0, 1) - position(2, 1)) * s[0] +
378  (position(1, 1) - position(2, 1)) * s[1];
379 
380  double A =
381  ((position(1, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(1, 1)) -
382  (position(0, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(0, 1)) +
383  (position(0, 0) * position(1, 1) - position(1, 0) * position(0, 1))) /
384  2.0;
385  double A0, A1, A2;
386  A0 =
387  ((position(1, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(1, 1)) -
388  (phi[0] * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * phi[1]) +
389  (phi[0] * position(1, 1) - position(1, 0) * phi[1])) /
390  2.0;
391  A1 =
392  ((phi[0] * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * phi[1]) -
393  (position(0, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(0, 1)) +
394  (position(0, 0) * phi[1] - phi[0] * position(0, 1))) /
395  2.0;
396  A2 =
397  ((position(1, 0) * phi[1] - phi[0] * position(1, 1)) -
398  (position(0, 0) * phi[1] - phi[0] * position(0, 1)) +
399  (position(0, 0) * position(1, 1) - position(1, 0) * position(0, 1))) /
400  2.0;
401 
402  // assigned area coordinates
403  Vector<double> xi(3);
404  xi[0] = A0 / A;
405  xi[1] = A1 / A;
406  xi[2] = A2 / A;
407 
408  Vector<double> b(3);
409  Vector<double> c(3);
410  Vector<double> lamb(3);
411  Vector<double> lamb_p(3);
412  Vector<double> pp(2);
413  Vector<double> a(2), cc(2);
414 
415  // compute for b and c
416  b[1] = position(0, 0) - position(2, 0);
417  b[2] = position(1, 0) - position(0, 0);
418  b[0] = position(2, 0) - position(1, 0);
419 
420  c[1] = position(2, 1) - position(0, 1);
421  c[2] = position(0, 1) - position(1, 1);
422  c[0] = position(1, 1) - position(2, 1);
423 
424  // compute for a point of perpendicular
425  // on the edge opposite to node0 (top vertex)
426  Vector<double> v(2);
427  v[0] = (position(2, 0) - position(1, 0));
428  v[1] = (position(2, 1) - position(1, 1));
429  double m = v[1] / v[0];
430  a[0] = position(1, 0);
431  a[1] = position(1, 1);
432  cc[0] = position(0, 0);
433  cc[1] = position(0, 1);
434  if (v[0] == 0)
435  {
436  m = v[0] / v[1];
437  pp[1] = (v[0] * m * a[1] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[0] * a[0] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
438  ((v[0] * m) + v[1]);
439  pp[0] = (pp[1] - a[1]) * m + a[0];
440  }
441  else
442  {
443  pp[0] = (v[1] * m * a[0] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[1] * a[1] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
444  (v[1] * m + v[0]);
445  pp[1] = m * (pp[0] - a[0]) + a[1];
446  }
447  double l = sqrt(v[0] * v[0] + v[1] * v[1]);
448  double l1 =
449  sqrt((pp[0] - a[0]) * (pp[0] - a[0]) + (pp[1] - a[1]) * (pp[1] - a[1]));
450  lamb_p[0] = l1 / l;
451  lamb[0] = 1 - lamb_p[0];
452 
453  // on the edge opposite to node1
454  v[0] = (position(0, 0) - position(2, 0));
455  v[1] = (position(0, 1) - position(2, 1));
456  m = v[1] / v[0];
457  a[0] = position(2, 0);
458  a[1] = position(2, 1);
459  cc[0] = position(1, 0);
460  cc[1] = position(1, 1);
461  if (v[0] == 0)
462  {
463  m = v[0] / v[1];
464  pp[1] = (v[0] * m * a[1] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[0] * a[0] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
465  ((v[0] * m) + v[1]);
466  pp[0] = (pp[1] - a[1]) * m + a[0];
467  }
468  else
469  {
470  pp[0] = (v[1] * m * a[0] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[1] * a[1] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
471  (v[1] * m + v[0]);
472  pp[1] = m * (pp[0] - a[0]) + a[1];
473  }
474  l = sqrt(v[0] * v[0] + v[1] * v[1]);
475  l1 =
476  sqrt((pp[0] - a[0]) * (pp[0] - a[0]) + (pp[1] - a[1]) * (pp[1] - a[1]));
477  lamb_p[1] = l1 / l;
478  lamb[1] = 1 - lamb_p[1];
479 
480  // on the edge opposite to node2 (right bottom)
481  v[0] = (position(1, 0) - position(0, 0));
482  v[1] = (position(1, 1) - position(0, 1));
483  m = v[1] / v[0];
484  a[0] = position(0, 0);
485  a[1] = position(0, 1);
486  cc[0] = position(2, 0);
487  cc[1] = position(2, 1);
488  if (v[0] == 0)
489  {
490  m = v[0] / v[1];
491  pp[1] = (v[0] * m * a[1] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[0] * a[0] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
492  ((v[0] * m) + v[1]);
493  pp[0] = (pp[1] - a[1]) * m + a[0];
494  }
495  else
496  {
497  pp[0] = (v[1] * m * a[0] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[1] * a[1] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
498  (v[1] * m + v[0]);
499  pp[1] = m * (pp[0] - a[0]) + a[1];
500  }
501  l = sqrt(v[0] * v[0] + v[1] * v[1]);
502  l1 =
503  sqrt((pp[0] - a[0]) * (pp[0] - a[0]) + (pp[1] - a[1]) * (pp[1] - a[1]));
504  lamb_p[2] = l1 / l;
505  lamb[2] = 1 - lamb_p[2];
506 
507 
508  Vector<double> dxids0(3, 0.0);
509  Vector<double> dxids1(3, 0.0);
510 
511  dxids0[0] = c[0] / A / 2.0;
512  dxids0[1] = c[1] / A / 2.0;
513  dxids0[2] = c[2] / A / 2.0;
514 
515  dxids1[0] = b[0] / A / 2.0;
516  dxids1[1] = b[1] / A / 2.0;
517  dxids1[2] = b[2] / A / 2.0;
518 
519  DShape psi1(3, 6, 3);
520  // define dshape functions that associated to dofs at node 0
521  psi1(0, 0, 0) =
522  5.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] +
523  5.0 * 4.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (xi[1] + xi[2]) +
524  10.0 * 3.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * (xi[1] + xi[2]) * (xi[1] + xi[2]) +
525  30.0 * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
526  (lamb[2] * xi[1] + lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
527  psi1(0, 1, 0) =
528  3.0 * b[0] * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[1] - xi[2]) +
529  3.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * (b[2] * xi[1] - b[1] * xi[2]) *
530  (xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2]) +
531  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (b[2] * xi[1] - b[1] * xi[2]) +
532  15 * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
533  (b[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] - b[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
534  psi1(0, 2, 0) =
535  -3.0 * c[0] * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[1] - xi[2]) -
536  3.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * (c[2] * xi[1] - c[1] * xi[2]) *
537  (xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2]) -
538  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (c[2] * xi[1] - c[1] * xi[2]) -
539  15.0 * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
540  (c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] - c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
541  psi1(0, 3, 0) =
542  1.0 / 2.0 * 3.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] *
543  (b[2] * b[2] * xi[1] * xi[1] + b[1] * b[1] * xi[2] * xi[2]) +
544  2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
545  (-b[1] * b[2] * xi[0] + b[2] * b[0] * xi[1] + b[0] * b[1] * xi[2]) +
546  5.0 / 2.0 * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
547  (b[2] * b[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] + b[1] * b[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]) +
548  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (-b[1] * b[2]);
549  psi1(0, 4, 0) =
550  1.0 / 2.0 * 3.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] *
551  (c[2] * c[2] * xi[1] * xi[1] + c[1] * c[1] * xi[2] * xi[2]) +
552  2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
553  (-c[1] * c[2] * xi[0] + c[2] * c[0] * xi[1] + c[0] * c[1] * xi[2]) +
554  5.0 / 2.0 * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
555  (c[2] * c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] + c[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]) +
556  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (-c[1] * c[2]);
557  psi1(0, 5, 0) =
558  b[0] * c[0] * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[0] + xi[1] + xi[2]) +
559  b[0] * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] +
560  b[1] * c[1] * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[2] *
561  (xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[1]) +
562  b[1] * c[1] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] * (-xi[1] - xi[2]) +
563  b[2] * c[2] * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] *
564  (xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[2] * xi[2]) +
565  b[2] * c[2] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (-xi[2] - xi[1]) -
566  5.0 * 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
567  (b[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2] + b[2] * c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1]);
568 
569  psi1(0, 0, 1) =
570  5.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] +
571  10.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * 2.0 * (xi[1] + xi[2]) +
572  30.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] * (lamb[2] * xi[1] + lamb_p[1] * xi[2]) +
573  30.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (lamb[2]);
574  psi1(0, 1, 1) =
575  3.0 * b[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] * (xi[1] - xi[2]) +
576  3.0 * b[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] +
577  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (b[2]) * (xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1] + 4 * xi[2]) +
578  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (b[2] * xi[1] - b[1] * xi[2]) * (4.0) +
579  15 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] *
580  (b[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] - b[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]) +
581  15 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (b[2] * lamb[2]);
582  psi1(0, 2, 1) =
583  -3.0 * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] * (xi[1] - xi[2]) -
584  3.0 * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] -
585  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (c[2] * xi[1] - c[1] * xi[2]) * (4.0) -
586  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (c[2]) * (xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2]) -
587  15.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (c[2] * lamb[2]) -
588  15.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] *
589  (c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] - c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
590  psi1(0, 3, 1) =
591  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (b[2] * b[2] * 2.0 * xi[1]) +
592  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (b[2] * b[0]) +
593  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] *
594  (-b[1] * b[2] * xi[0] + b[2] * b[0] * xi[1] + b[0] * b[1] * xi[2]) +
595  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (b[2] * b[2] * lamb[2]) +
596  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] *
597  (b[2] * b[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] + b[1] * b[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
598  psi1(0, 4, 1) =
599  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (c[2] * c[2] * 2.0 * xi[1]) +
600  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (c[2] * c[0]) +
601  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] *
602  (-c[1] * c[2] * xi[0] + c[2] * c[0] * xi[1] + c[0] * c[1] * xi[2]) +
603  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (c[2] * c[2] * lamb[2]) +
604  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] *
605  (c[2] * c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] + c[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
606  psi1(0, 5, 1) =
607  b[0] * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] +
608  b[0] * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] * (xi[0] + xi[1] + xi[2]) +
609  b[1] * c[1] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] * (xi[2] - xi[0] - 2.0 * xi[1]) +
610  b[2] * c[2] * xi[0] * xi[0] *
611  (xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[2] * xi[2]) +
612  b[2] * c[2] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[2] - xi[0]) -
613  5.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] *
614  (b[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2] + b[2] * c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1]) -
615  5.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (b[2] * c[2] * lamb[2]);
616 
617  psi1(0, 0, 2) =
618  5.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] +
619  10.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * 2.0 * (xi[1] + xi[2]) +
620  30.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (lamb_p[1]) +
621  30.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (lamb[2] * xi[1] + lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
622  psi1(0, 1, 2) =
623  3.0 * b[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (-1.0) +
624  3.0 * b[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[1] - xi[2]) +
625  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (b[2] * xi[1] - b[1] * xi[2]) * (4.0) +
626  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (-b[1]) * (xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1] + 4 * xi[2]) +
627  15 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (-b[1] * lamb_p[1]) +
628  15 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
629  (b[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] - b[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
630  psi1(0, 2, 2) =
631  -3.0 * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (-1.0) +
632  -3.0 * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[1] - xi[2]) -
633  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (c[2] * xi[1] - c[1] * xi[2]) * (4.0) -
634  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (-1.0 * c[1]) *
635  (xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2]) -
636  15.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (-1.0 * c[1] * lamb_p[1]) -
637  15.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
638  (c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] - c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
639  psi1(0, 3, 2) =
640  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (b[1] * b[1] * 2.0 * xi[2]) +
641  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (b[0] * b[1]) +
642  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
643  (-b[1] * b[2] * xi[0] + b[2] * b[0] * xi[1] + b[0] * b[1] * xi[2]) +
644  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (b[1] * b[1] * lamb_p[1]) +
645  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
646  (b[2] * b[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] + b[1] * b[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
647  psi1(0, 4, 2) =
648  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * (c[1] * c[1] * 2.0 * xi[2]) +
649  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (c[0] * c[1]) +
650  xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
651  (-c[1] * c[2] * xi[0] + c[2] * c[0] * xi[1] + c[0] * c[1] * xi[2]) +
652  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (c[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1]) +
653  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
654  (c[2] * c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1] + c[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2]);
655  psi1(0, 5, 2) =
656  b[0] * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] +
657  b[0] * c[0] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[0] + xi[1] + xi[2]) +
658  b[1] * c[1] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[2] * (xi[1] - xi[0]) +
659  b[1] * c[1] * xi[0] * xi[0] *
660  (xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[1]) +
661  b[2] * c[2] * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[1] - xi[0] - 2.0 * xi[2]) -
662  5.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (b[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1]) -
663  5.0 * xi[0] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
664  (b[1] * c[1] * lamb_p[1] * xi[2] + b[2] * c[2] * lamb[2] * xi[1]);
665 
666  // by chain rule, we can obtain dshape wrt s0 at node0
667  dpsids(0, 0, 0) = psi1(0, 0, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(0, 0, 1) * dxids0[1] +
668  psi1(0, 0, 2) * dxids0[2];
669  dpsids(0, 1, 0) = psi1(0, 1, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(0, 1, 1) * dxids0[1] +
670  psi1(0, 1, 2) * dxids0[2];
671  dpsids(0, 2, 0) = psi1(0, 2, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(0, 2, 1) * dxids0[1] +
672  psi1(0, 2, 2) * dxids0[2];
673  dpsids(0, 3, 0) = psi1(0, 3, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(0, 3, 1) * dxids0[1] +
674  psi1(0, 3, 2) * dxids0[2];
675  dpsids(0, 4, 0) = psi1(0, 4, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(0, 4, 1) * dxids0[1] +
676  psi1(0, 4, 2) * dxids0[2];
677  dpsids(0, 5, 0) = psi1(0, 5, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(0, 5, 1) * dxids0[1] +
678  psi1(0, 5, 2) * dxids0[2];
679 
680  // by chain rule, we can obtain dshape wrt s1 at node0
681  dpsids(0, 0, 1) = psi1(0, 0, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(0, 0, 1) * dxids1[1] +
682  psi1(0, 0, 2) * dxids1[2];
683  dpsids(0, 1, 1) = psi1(0, 1, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(0, 1, 1) * dxids1[1] +
684  psi1(0, 1, 2) * dxids1[2];
685  dpsids(0, 2, 1) = psi1(0, 2, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(0, 2, 1) * dxids1[1] +
686  psi1(0, 2, 2) * dxids1[2];
687  dpsids(0, 3, 1) = psi1(0, 3, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(0, 3, 1) * dxids1[1] +
688  psi1(0, 3, 2) * dxids1[2];
689  dpsids(0, 4, 1) = psi1(0, 4, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(0, 4, 1) * dxids1[1] +
690  psi1(0, 4, 2) * dxids1[2];
691  dpsids(0, 5, 1) = psi1(0, 5, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(0, 5, 1) * dxids1[1] +
692  psi1(0, 5, 2) * dxids1[2];
693  //-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
694  // define shape functions that associated to dofs at node 1
695  // wrt area coordinate 1
696  psi1(1, 0, 1) =
697  5.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] +
698  5.0 * 4.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (xi[2] + xi[0]) +
699  10.0 * 3.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * (xi[2] + xi[0]) * (xi[2] + xi[0]) +
700  30.0 * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
701  (lamb[0] * xi[2] + lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
702  psi1(1, 1, 1) =
703  3.0 * b[1] * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[2] - xi[0]) +
704  3.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * (b[0] * xi[2] - b[2] * xi[0]) *
705  (xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0]) +
706  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (b[0] * xi[2] - b[2] * xi[0]) +
707  15 * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
708  (b[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] - b[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
709  psi1(1, 2, 1) =
710  -3.0 * c[1] * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[2] - xi[0]) -
711  3.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * (c[0] * xi[2] - c[2] * xi[0]) *
712  (xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0]) -
713  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (c[0] * xi[2] - c[2] * xi[0]) -
714  15.0 * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
715  (c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] - c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
716  psi1(1, 3, 1) =
717  1.0 / 2.0 * 3.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] *
718  (b[0] * b[0] * xi[2] * xi[2] + b[2] * b[2] * xi[0] * xi[0]) +
719  2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
720  (-b[2] * b[0] * xi[1] + b[0] * b[1] * xi[2] + b[1] * b[2] * xi[0]) +
721  5.0 / 2.0 * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
722  (b[0] * b[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] + b[2] * b[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]) +
723  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (-b[2]) * b[0];
724  psi1(1, 4, 1) =
725  1.0 / 2.0 * 3.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] *
726  (c[0] * c[0] * xi[2] * xi[2] + c[2] * c[2] * xi[0] * xi[0]) +
727  2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
728  (-c[2] * c[0] * xi[1] + c[0] * c[1] * xi[2] + c[1] * c[2] * xi[0]) +
729  5.0 / 2.0 * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
730  (c[0] * c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] + c[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]) +
731  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (-c[2]) * c[0];
732  psi1(1, 5, 1) =
733  b[1] * c[1] * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[1] + xi[2] + xi[0]) +
734  b[1] * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] +
735  b[2] * c[2] * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[0] *
736  (xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[2]) +
737  b[2] * c[2] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] * (-xi[2] - xi[0]) +
738  b[0] * c[0] * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] *
739  (xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[0] * xi[0]) +
740  b[0] * c[0] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (-xi[0] - xi[2]) -
741  5.0 * 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
742  (b[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0] + b[0] * c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2]);
743 
744  // wrt area coordinate2
745  psi1(1, 0, 2) =
746  5.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] +
747  10.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * 2.0 * (xi[2] + xi[0]) +
748  30.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] * (lamb[0] * xi[2] + lamb_p[2] * xi[0]) +
749  30.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (lamb[0]);
750  psi1(1, 1, 2) =
751  3.0 * b[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] * (xi[2] - xi[0]) +
752  3.0 * b[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] +
753  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (b[0]) * (xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0]) +
754  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (b[0] * xi[2] - b[2] * xi[0]) * (4.0) +
755  15.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] *
756  (b[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] - b[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]) +
757  15 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (b[0] * lamb[0]);
758  psi1(1, 2, 2) =
759  -3.0 * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] +
760  -3.0 * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] * (xi[2] - xi[0]) -
761  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (c[0] * xi[2] - c[2] * xi[0]) * (4.0) -
762  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (c[0]) * (xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0]) -
763  15.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (c[0] * lamb[0]) -
764  15.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] *
765  (c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] - c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
766  psi1(1, 3, 2) =
767  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (b[0] * b[0] * 2.0 * xi[2]) +
768  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (b[0] * b[1]) +
769  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] *
770  (-b[2] * b[0] * xi[1] + b[0] * b[1] * xi[2] + b[1] * b[2] * xi[0]) +
771  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (b[0] * b[0] * lamb[0]) +
772  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] *
773  (b[0] * b[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] + b[2] * b[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
774  psi1(1, 4, 2) =
775  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (c[0] * c[0] * 2.0 * xi[2]) +
776  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (c[0] * c[1]) +
777  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] *
778  (-c[2] * c[0] * xi[1] + c[0] * c[1] * xi[2] + c[1] * c[2] * xi[0]) +
779  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (c[0] * c[0] * lamb[0]) +
780  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] *
781  (c[0] * c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] + c[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
782  psi1(1, 5, 2) =
783  b[1] * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] +
784  b[1] * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] * (xi[1] + xi[2] + xi[0]) +
785  b[2] * c[2] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] * (xi[0] - xi[1] - 2.0 * xi[2]) +
786  b[0] * c[0] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[0] - xi[1]) +
787  b[0] * c[0] * xi[1] * xi[1] *
788  (xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[0] * xi[0]) -
789  5.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (b[0] * c[0] * lamb[0]) -
790  5.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] *
791  (b[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0] + b[0] * c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2]);
792 
793  // wrt area coordinate0
794  psi1(1, 0, 0) =
795  5.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] +
796  10.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * 2.0 * (xi[2] + xi[0]) +
797  30.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (lamb_p[2]) +
798  30.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (lamb[0] * xi[2] + lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
799  psi1(1, 1, 0) =
800  -3.0 * b[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] +
801  3.0 * b[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[2] - xi[0]) +
802  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (b[0] * xi[2] - b[2] * xi[0]) * (4.0) +
803  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (-b[2]) * (xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0]) -
804  15 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (b[2] * lamb_p[2]) +
805  15 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
806  (b[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] - b[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
807  psi1(1, 2, 0) =
808  3.0 * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] -
809  3.0 * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[2] - xi[0]) -
810  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (c[0] * xi[2] - c[2] * xi[0]) * (4.0) -
811  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (-c[2]) * (xi[1] + 4.0 * xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0]) +
812  15.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (c[2] * lamb_p[2]) -
813  15.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
814  (c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] - c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
815  psi1(1, 3, 0) =
816  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (b[2] * b[2] * 2.0 * xi[0]) +
817  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (b[1] * b[2]) +
818  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
819  (-b[2] * b[0] * xi[1] + b[0] * b[1] * xi[2] + b[1] * b[2] * xi[0]) +
820  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (b[2] * b[2] * lamb_p[2]) +
821  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
822  (b[0] * b[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] + b[2] * b[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
823  psi1(1, 4, 0) =
824  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * (c[2] * c[2] * 2.0 * xi[0]) +
825  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (c[1] * c[2]) +
826  xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
827  (-c[2] * c[0] * xi[1] + c[0] * c[1] * xi[2] + c[1] * c[2] * xi[0]) +
828  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (c[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2]) +
829  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
830  (c[0] * c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2] + c[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0]);
831  psi1(1, 5, 0) =
832  b[1] * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] +
833  b[1] * c[1] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[1] + xi[2] + xi[0]) +
834  b[2] * c[2] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[0] * (xi[2] - xi[1]) +
835  b[2] * c[2] * xi[1] * xi[1] *
836  (xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[2]) +
837  b[0] * c[0] * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * (xi[2] - xi[1] - 2.0 * xi[0]) -
838  5.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (b[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2]) -
839  5.0 * xi[1] * xi[1] * xi[2] *
840  (b[2] * c[2] * lamb_p[2] * xi[0] + b[0] * c[0] * lamb[0] * xi[2]);
841  //--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
842  // by chain rule, we can obtain dshape wrt s0 at node1
843  dpsids(1, 0, 0) = psi1(1, 0, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(1, 0, 1) * dxids0[1] +
844  psi1(1, 0, 2) * dxids0[2];
845  dpsids(1, 1, 0) = psi1(1, 1, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(1, 1, 1) * dxids0[1] +
846  psi1(1, 1, 2) * dxids0[2];
847  dpsids(1, 2, 0) = psi1(1, 2, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(1, 2, 1) * dxids0[1] +
848  psi1(1, 2, 2) * dxids0[2];
849  dpsids(1, 3, 0) = psi1(1, 3, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(1, 3, 1) * dxids0[1] +
850  psi1(1, 3, 2) * dxids0[2];
851  dpsids(1, 4, 0) = psi1(1, 4, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(1, 4, 1) * dxids0[1] +
852  psi1(1, 4, 2) * dxids0[2];
853  dpsids(1, 5, 0) = psi1(1, 5, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(1, 5, 1) * dxids0[1] +
854  psi1(1, 5, 2) * dxids0[2];
855 
856  // by chain rule, we can obtain dshape wrt s1 at node1
857  dpsids(1, 0, 1) = psi1(1, 0, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(1, 0, 1) * dxids1[1] +
858  psi1(1, 0, 2) * dxids1[2];
859  dpsids(1, 1, 1) = psi1(1, 1, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(1, 1, 1) * dxids1[1] +
860  psi1(1, 1, 2) * dxids1[2];
861  dpsids(1, 2, 1) = psi1(1, 2, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(1, 2, 1) * dxids1[1] +
862  psi1(1, 2, 2) * dxids1[2];
863  dpsids(1, 3, 1) = psi1(1, 3, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(1, 3, 1) * dxids1[1] +
864  psi1(1, 3, 2) * dxids1[2];
865  dpsids(1, 4, 1) = psi1(1, 4, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(1, 4, 1) * dxids1[1] +
866  psi1(1, 4, 2) * dxids1[2];
867  dpsids(1, 5, 1) = psi1(1, 5, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(1, 5, 1) * dxids1[1] +
868  psi1(1, 5, 2) * dxids1[2];
869  //-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
870  // define shape functions that associated to dofs at node 2
871  // wrt area coordinate0
872  psi1(2, 0, 0) =
873  5.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] +
874  10.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * 2.0 * (xi[0] + xi[1]) +
875  30.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] * (lamb[1] * xi[0] + lamb_p[0] * xi[1]) +
876  30.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (lamb[1]);
877  psi1(2, 1, 0) =
878  3.0 * b[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] * (xi[0] - xi[1]) +
879  3.0 * b[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] +
880  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (b[1]) * (xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1]) +
881  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (b[1] * xi[0] - b[0] * xi[1]) * (4.0) +
882  15.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] *
883  (b[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] - b[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]) +
884  15.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (b[1] * lamb[1]);
885  psi1(2, 2, 0) =
886  -3.0 * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] +
887  -3.0 * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] * (xi[0] - xi[1]) -
888  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (c[1] * xi[0] - c[0] * xi[1]) * (4.0) -
889  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (c[1]) * (xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1]) -
890  15.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (c[1] * lamb[1]) -
891  15.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] *
892  (c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] - c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
893  psi1(2, 3, 0) =
894  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (b[1] * b[1] * 2.0 * xi[0]) +
895  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (b[1] * b[2]) +
896  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] *
897  (-b[0] * b[1] * xi[2] + b[1] * b[2] * xi[0] + b[2] * b[0] * xi[1]) +
898  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (b[1] * b[1] * lamb[1]) +
899  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] *
900  (b[1] * b[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] + b[0] * b[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
901  psi1(2, 4, 0) =
902  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (c[1] * c[1] * 2.0 * xi[0]) +
903  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (c[1] * c[2]) +
904  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] *
905  (-c[0] * c[1] * xi[2] + c[1] * c[2] * xi[0] + c[2] * c[0] * xi[1]) +
906  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (c[1] * c[1] * lamb[1]) +
907  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] *
908  (c[1] * c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] + c[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
909  psi1(2, 5, 0) =
910  b[2] * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] +
911  b[2] * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] * (xi[2] + xi[0] + xi[1]) +
912  b[0] * c[0] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] * (xi[1] - xi[2] - 2.0 * xi[0]) +
913  b[1] * c[1] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[1] - xi[2]) +
914  b[1] * c[1] * xi[2] * xi[2] *
915  (xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[1] * xi[1]) -
916  5.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (b[1] * c[1] * lamb[1]) -
917  5.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] *
918  (b[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1] + b[1] * c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0]);
919 
920  // wrt area coordinate1
921  psi1(2, 0, 1) =
922  5.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] +
923  10.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * 2.0 * (xi[0] + xi[1]) +
924  30.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (lamb_p[0]) +
925  30.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (lamb[1] * xi[0] + lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
926  psi1(2, 1, 1) =
927  3.0 * b[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (-1.0) +
928  3.0 * b[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[0] - xi[1]) +
929  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (-b[0]) * (xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1]) +
930  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (b[1] * xi[0] - b[0] * xi[1]) * (4.0) +
931  15 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
932  (b[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] - b[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]) +
933  15.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (-b[0] * lamb_p[0]);
934  psi1(2, 2, 1) =
935  -3.0 * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (-1.0) +
936  -3.0 * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[0] - xi[1]) -
937  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (c[1] * xi[0] - c[0] * xi[1]) * (4.0) -
938  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (-1.0 * c[0]) *
939  (xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1]) -
940  15.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (-1.0 * c[0] * lamb_p[0]) -
941  15.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
942  (c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] - c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
943  psi1(2, 3, 1) =
944  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (b[0] * b[0] * 2.0 * xi[1]) +
945  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (b[2] * b[0]) +
946  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
947  (-b[0] * b[1] * xi[2] + b[1] * b[2] * xi[0] + b[2] * b[0] * xi[1]) +
948  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (b[0] * b[0] * lamb_p[0]) +
949  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
950  (b[1] * b[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] + b[0] * b[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
951  psi1(2, 4, 1) =
952  1.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (c[0] * c[0] * 2.0 * xi[1]) +
953  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (c[2] * c[0]) +
954  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
955  (-c[0] * c[1] * xi[2] + c[1] * c[2] * xi[0] + c[2] * c[0] * xi[1]) +
956  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (c[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0]) +
957  5.0 / 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
958  (c[1] * c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] + c[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
959  psi1(2, 5, 1) =
960  b[2] * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] +
961  b[2] * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[2] + xi[0] + xi[1]) +
962  b[0] * c[0] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] * (xi[0] - xi[2]) +
963  b[0] * c[0] * xi[2] * xi[2] *
964  (xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[0]) +
965  b[1] * c[1] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (xi[0] - xi[2] - 2.0 * xi[1]) -
966  5.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (b[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0]) -
967  5.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] *
968  (b[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1] + b[1] * c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0]);
969 
970  // wrt area coordinate2
971  psi1(2, 0, 2) =
972  5.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] +
973  5.0 * 4.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (xi[0] + xi[1]) +
974  10.0 * 3.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * (xi[0] + xi[1]) * (xi[0] + xi[1]) +
975  30.0 * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
976  (lamb[1] * xi[0] + lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
977  psi1(2, 1, 2) =
978  3.0 * b[2] * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[0] - xi[1]) +
979  3.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * (b[1] * xi[0] - b[0] * xi[1]) *
980  (xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1]) +
981  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (b[1] * xi[0] - b[0] * xi[1]) +
982  15 * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
983  (b[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] - b[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
984  psi1(2, 2, 2) =
985  -3.0 * c[2] * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[0] - xi[1]) -
986  3.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] * (c[1] * xi[0] - c[0] * xi[1]) *
987  (xi[2] + 4.0 * xi[0] + 4.0 * xi[1]) -
988  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * (c[1] * xi[0] - c[0] * xi[1]) -
989  15.0 * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
990  (c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] - c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]);
991  psi1(2, 3, 2) =
992  1.0 / 2.0 * 3.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] *
993  (b[1] * b[1] * xi[0] * xi[0] + b[0] * b[0] * xi[1] * xi[1]) +
994  2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
995  (-b[0] * b[1] * xi[2] + b[1] * b[2] * xi[0] + b[2] * b[0] * xi[1]) +
996  5.0 / 2.0 * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
997  (b[1] * b[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] + b[0] * b[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]) +
998  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (-b[0]) * b[1];
999  psi1(2, 4, 2) =
1000  1.0 / 2.0 * 3.0 * xi[2] * xi[2] *
1001  (c[1] * c[1] * xi[0] * xi[0] + c[0] * c[0] * xi[1] * xi[1]) +
1002  2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
1003  (-c[0] * c[1] * xi[2] + c[1] * c[2] * xi[0] + c[2] * c[0] * xi[1]) +
1004  5.0 / 2.0 * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
1005  (c[1] * c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0] + c[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1]) +
1006  xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (-c[0] * c[1]);
1007  psi1(2, 5, 2) =
1008  b[2] * c[2] * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] * (xi[2] + xi[0] + xi[1]) +
1009  b[2] * c[2] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] +
1010  b[0] * c[0] * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[1] *
1011  (xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[0] * xi[0]) +
1012  b[0] * c[0] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[1] * (-xi[0] - xi[1]) +
1013  b[1] * c[1] * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] *
1014  (xi[0] * xi[1] - xi[1] * xi[2] - xi[2] * xi[0] - xi[1] * xi[1]) +
1015  b[1] * c[1] * xi[2] * xi[2] * xi[0] * (-xi[1] - xi[0]) -
1016  5.0 * 2.0 * xi[2] * xi[0] * xi[1] *
1017  (b[0] * c[0] * lamb_p[0] * xi[1] + b[1] * c[1] * lamb[1] * xi[0]);
1018 
1019  // by chain rule, we can obtain dshape wrt s0 at node2
1020  dpsids(2, 0, 0) = psi1(2, 0, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(2, 0, 1) * dxids0[1] +
1021  psi1(2, 0, 2) * dxids0[2];
1022  dpsids(2, 1, 0) = psi1(2, 1, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(2, 1, 1) * dxids0[1] +
1023  psi1(2, 1, 2) * dxids0[2];
1024  dpsids(2, 2, 0) = psi1(2, 2, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(2, 2, 1) * dxids0[1] +
1025  psi1(2, 2, 2) * dxids0[2];
1026  dpsids(2, 3, 0) = psi1(2, 3, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(2, 3, 1) * dxids0[1] +
1027  psi1(2, 3, 2) * dxids0[2];
1028  dpsids(2, 4, 0) = psi1(2, 4, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(2, 4, 1) * dxids0[1] +
1029  psi1(2, 4, 2) * dxids0[2];
1030  dpsids(2, 5, 0) = psi1(2, 5, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi1(2, 5, 1) * dxids0[1] +
1031  psi1(2, 5, 2) * dxids0[2];
1032 
1033  // by chain rule, we can obtain dshape wrt s1 at node2
1034  dpsids(2, 0, 1) = psi1(2, 0, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(2, 0, 1) * dxids1[1] +
1035  psi1(2, 0, 2) * dxids1[2];
1036  dpsids(2, 1, 1) = psi1(2, 1, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(2, 1, 1) * dxids1[1] +
1037  psi1(2, 1, 2) * dxids1[2];
1038  dpsids(2, 2, 1) = psi1(2, 2, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(2, 2, 1) * dxids1[1] +
1039  psi1(2, 2, 2) * dxids1[2];
1040  dpsids(2, 3, 1) = psi1(2, 3, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(2, 3, 1) * dxids1[1] +
1041  psi1(2, 3, 2) * dxids1[2];
1042  dpsids(2, 4, 1) = psi1(2, 4, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(2, 4, 1) * dxids1[1] +
1043  psi1(2, 4, 2) * dxids1[2];
1044  dpsids(2, 5, 1) = psi1(2, 5, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi1(2, 5, 1) * dxids1[1] +
1045  psi1(2, 5, 2) * dxids1[2];
1046  }
1047 
1048  void d2Bshape_local(const Vector<double>& s,
1049  Shape& psi,
1050  DShape& dpsids,
1051  DShape& d2psids,
1052  DenseMatrix<double>& position) const
1053  {
1054  // assign for dshape functions
1055  dBshape_local(s, psi, dpsids, position);
1056  //---------------------------------------------
1057  // the mapping to physical coordinates
1058  //----------------------------------------------
1059  Vector<double> phi(2);
1060  phi[0] = position(2, 0) + (position(0, 0) - position(2, 0)) * s[0] +
1061  (position(1, 0) - position(2, 0)) * s[1];
1062  phi[1] = position(2, 1) + (position(0, 1) - position(2, 1)) * s[0] +
1063  (position(1, 1) - position(2, 1)) * s[1];
1064 
1065  double A =
1066  ((position(1, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(1, 1)) -
1067  (position(0, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(0, 1)) +
1068  (position(0, 0) * position(1, 1) - position(1, 0) * position(0, 1))) /
1069  2.0;
1070  double A0, A1, A2;
1071  A0 =
1072  ((position(1, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(1, 1)) -
1073  (phi[0] * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * phi[1]) +
1074  (phi[0] * position(1, 1) - position(1, 0) * phi[1])) /
1075  2.0;
1076  A1 =
1077  ((phi[0] * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * phi[1]) -
1078  (position(0, 0) * position(2, 1) - position(2, 0) * position(0, 1)) +
1079  (position(0, 0) * phi[1] - phi[0] * position(0, 1))) /
1080  2.0;
1081  A2 =
1082  ((position(1, 0) * phi[1] - phi[0] * position(1, 1)) -
1083  (position(0, 0) * phi[1] - phi[0] * position(0, 1)) +
1084  (position(0, 0) * position(1, 1) - position(1, 0) * position(0, 1))) /
1085  2.0;
1086 
1087  // assigned area coordinates
1088  Vector<double> xi(3);
1089  xi[0] = A0 / A;
1090  xi[1] = A1 / A;
1091  xi[2] = A2 / A;
1092 
1093  Vector<double> b(3);
1094  Vector<double> c(3);
1095  Vector<double> lamb(3);
1096  Vector<double> lamb_p(3);
1097  Vector<double> pp(2);
1098  Vector<double> a(2), cc(2);
1099 
1100  // compute for b and c
1101  b[1] = position(0, 0) - position(2, 0);
1102  b[2] = position(1, 0) - position(0, 0);
1103  b[0] = position(2, 0) - position(1, 0);
1104 
1105  c[1] = position(2, 1) - position(0, 1);
1106  c[2] = position(0, 1) - position(1, 1);
1107  c[0] = position(1, 1) - position(2, 1);
1108 
1109  // compute for a point of perpendicular
1110  // on the edge opposite to node0 (top vertex)
1111  Vector<double> v(2);
1112  v[0] = (position(2, 0) - position(1, 0));
1113  v[1] = (position(2, 1) - position(1, 1));
1114  double m = v[1] / v[0];
1115  a[0] = position(1, 0);
1116  a[1] = position(1, 1);
1117  cc[0] = position(0, 0);
1118  cc[1] = position(0, 1);
1119  if (v[0] == 0)
1120  {
1121  m = v[0] / v[1];
1122  pp[1] = (v[0] * m * a[1] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[0] * a[0] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
1123  ((v[0] * m) + v[1]);
1124  pp[0] = (pp[1] - a[1]) * m + a[0];
1125  }
1126  else
1127  {
1128  pp[0] = (v[1] * m * a[0] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[1] * a[1] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
1129  (v[1] * m + v[0]);
1130  pp[1] = m * (pp[0] - a[0]) + a[1];
1131  }
1132  double l = sqrt(v[0] * v[0] + v[1] * v[1]);
1133  double l1 =
1134  sqrt((pp[0] - a[0]) * (pp[0] - a[0]) + (pp[1] - a[1]) * (pp[1] - a[1]));
1135  lamb_p[0] = l1 / l;
1136  lamb[0] = 1 - lamb_p[0];
1137 
1138  // on the edge opposite to node1
1139  v[0] = (position(0, 0) - position(2, 0));
1140  v[1] = (position(0, 1) - position(2, 1));
1141  m = v[1] / v[0];
1142  a[0] = position(2, 0);
1143  a[1] = position(2, 1);
1144  cc[0] = position(1, 0);
1145  cc[1] = position(1, 1);
1146  if (v[0] == 0)
1147  {
1148  m = v[0] / v[1];
1149  pp[1] = (v[0] * m * a[1] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[0] * a[0] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
1150  ((v[0] * m) + v[1]);
1151  pp[0] = (pp[1] - a[1]) * m + a[0];
1152  }
1153  else
1154  {
1155  pp[0] = (v[1] * m * a[0] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[1] * a[1] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
1156  (v[1] * m + v[0]);
1157  pp[1] = m * (pp[0] - a[0]) + a[1];
1158  }
1159  l = sqrt(v[0] * v[0] + v[1] * v[1]);
1160  l1 =
1161  sqrt((pp[0] - a[0]) * (pp[0] - a[0]) + (pp[1] - a[1]) * (pp[1] - a[1]));
1162  lamb_p[1] = l1 / l;
1163  lamb[1] = 1 - lamb_p[1];
1164 
1165  // on the edge opposite to node2 (right bottom)
1166  v[0] = (position(1, 0) - position(0, 0));
1167  v[1] = (position(1, 1) - position(0, 1));
1168  m = v[1] / v[0];
1169  a[0] = position(0, 0);
1170  a[1] = position(0, 1);
1171  cc[0] = position(2, 0);
1172  cc[1] = position(2, 1);
1173  if (v[0] == 0)
1174  {
1175  m = v[0] / v[1];
1176  pp[1] = (v[0] * m * a[1] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[0] * a[0] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
1177  ((v[0] * m) + v[1]);
1178  pp[0] = (pp[1] - a[1]) * m + a[0];
1179  }
1180  else
1181  {
1182  pp[0] = (v[1] * m * a[0] + v[1] * cc[1] - v[1] * a[1] + v[0] * cc[0]) /
1183  (v[1] * m + v[0]);
1184  pp[1] = m * (pp[0] - a[0]) + a[1];
1185  }
1186  l = sqrt(v[0] * v[0] + v[1] * v[1]);
1187  l1 =
1188  sqrt((pp[0] - a[0]) * (pp[0] - a[0]) + (pp[1] - a[1]) * (pp[1] - a[1]));
1189  lamb_p[2] = l1 / l;
1190  lamb[2] = 1 - lamb_p[2];

1196  dxids0[1] = c[1] / A / 2.0;
1197  dxids0[2] = c[2] / A / 2.0;

1200  dxids1[1] = b[1] / A / 2.0;
1201  dxids1[2] = b[2] / A / 2.0;

2473  psi2(2, 0, 5) * dxids1[2]) *
2474  dxids1[1] +
2475  (psi2(2, 0, 4) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 0, 5) * dxids1[1] +
2476  psi2(2, 0, 2) * dxids1[2]) *
2477  dxids1[2];
2478  d2psids(2, 1, 1) =
2479  (psi2(2, 1, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 1, 3) * dxids1[1] +
2480  psi2(2, 1, 4) * dxids1[2]) *
2481  dxids1[0] +
2482  (psi2(2, 1, 3) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 1, 1) * dxids1[1] +
2483  psi2(2, 1, 5) * dxids1[2]) *
2484  dxids1[1] +
2485  (psi2(2, 1, 4) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 1, 5) * dxids1[1] +
2486  psi2(2, 1, 2) * dxids1[2]) *
2487  dxids1[2];
2488  d2psids(2, 2, 1) =
2489  (psi2(2, 2, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 2, 3) * dxids1[1] +
2490  psi2(2, 2, 4) * dxids1[2]) *
2491  dxids1[0] +
2492  (psi2(2, 2, 3) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 2, 1) * dxids1[1] +
2493  psi2(2, 2, 5) * dxids1[2]) *
2494  dxids1[1] +
2495  (psi2(2, 2, 4) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 2, 5) * dxids1[1] +
2496  psi2(2, 2, 2) * dxids1[2]) *
2497  dxids1[2];
2498  d2psids(2, 3, 1) =
2499  (psi2(2, 3, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 3, 3) * dxids1[1] +
2500  psi2(2, 3, 4) * dxids1[2]) *
2501  dxids1[0] +
2502  (psi2(2, 3, 3) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 3, 1) * dxids1[1] +
2503  psi2(2, 3, 5) * dxids1[2]) *
2504  dxids1[1] +
2505  (psi2(2, 3, 4) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 3, 5) * dxids1[1] +
2506  psi2(2, 3, 2) * dxids1[2]) *
2507  dxids1[2];
2508  d2psids(2, 4, 1) =
2509  (psi2(2, 4, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 4, 3) * dxids1[1] +
2510  psi2(2, 4, 4) * dxids1[2]) *
2511  dxids1[0] +
2512  (psi2(2, 4, 3) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 4, 1) * dxids1[1] +
2513  psi2(2, 4, 5) * dxids1[2]) *
2514  dxids1[1] +
2515  (psi2(2, 4, 4) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 4, 5) * dxids1[1] +
2516  psi2(2, 4, 2) * dxids1[2]) *
2517  dxids1[2];
2518  d2psids(2, 5, 1) =
2519  (psi2(2, 5, 0) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 5, 3) * dxids1[1] +
2520  psi2(2, 5, 4) * dxids1[2]) *
2521  dxids1[0] +
2522  (psi2(2, 5, 3) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 5, 1) * dxids1[1] +
2523  psi2(2, 5, 5) * dxids1[2]) *
2524  dxids1[1] +
2525  (psi2(2, 5, 4) * dxids1[0] + psi2(2, 5, 5) * dxids1[1] +
2526  psi2(2, 5, 2) * dxids1[2]) *
2527  dxids1[2];
2528 
2529  // by chain rule, we can obtain d2shape wrt s0s1 at node2
2530  d2psids(2, 0, 2) =
2531  (psi2(2, 0, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 0, 3) * dxids0[1] +
2532  psi2(2, 0, 4) * dxids0[2]) *
2533  dxids1[0] +
2534  (psi2(2, 0, 3) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 0, 1) * dxids0[1] +
2535  psi2(2, 0, 5) * dxids0[2]) *
2536  dxids1[1] +
2537  (psi2(2, 0, 4) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 0, 5) * dxids0[1] +
2538  psi2(2, 0, 2) * dxids0[2]) *
2539  dxids1[2];
2540  d2psids(2, 1, 2) =
2541  (psi2(2, 1, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 1, 3) * dxids0[1] +
2542  psi2(2, 1, 4) * dxids0[2]) *
2543  dxids1[0] +
2544  (psi2(2, 1, 3) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 1, 1) * dxids0[1] +
2545  psi2(2, 1, 5) * dxids0[2]) *
2546  dxids1[1] +
2547  (psi2(2, 1, 4) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 1, 5) * dxids0[1] +
2548  psi2(2, 1, 2) * dxids0[2]) *
2549  dxids1[2];
2550  d2psids(2, 2, 2) =
2551  (psi2(2, 2, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 2, 3) * dxids0[1] +
2552  psi2(2, 2, 4) * dxids0[2]) *
2553  dxids1[0] +
2554  (psi2(2, 2, 3) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 2, 1) * dxids0[1] +
2555  psi2(2, 2, 5) * dxids0[2]) *
2556  dxids1[1] +
2557  (psi2(2, 2, 4) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 2, 5) * dxids0[1] +
2558  psi2(2, 2, 2) * dxids0[2]) *
2559  dxids1[2];
2560  d2psids(2, 3, 2) =
2561  (psi2(2, 3, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 3, 3) * dxids0[1] +
2562  psi2(2, 3, 4) * dxids0[2]) *
2563  dxids1[0] +
2564  (psi2(2, 3, 3) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 3, 1) * dxids0[1] +
2565  psi2(2, 3, 5) * dxids0[2]) *
2566  dxids1[1] +
2567  (psi2(2, 3, 4) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 3, 5) * dxids0[1] +
2568  psi2(2, 3, 2) * dxids0[2]) *
2569  dxids1[2];
2570  d2psids(2, 4, 2) =
2571  (psi2(2, 4, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 4, 3) * dxids0[1] +
2572  psi2(2, 4, 4) * dxids0[2]) *
2573  dxids1[0] +
2574  (psi2(2, 4, 3) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 4, 1) * dxids0[1] +
2575  psi2(2, 4, 5) * dxids0[2]) *
2576  dxids1[1] +
2577  (psi2(2, 4, 4) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 4, 5) * dxids0[1] +
2578  psi2(2, 4, 2) * dxids0[2]) *
2579  dxids1[2];
2580  d2psids(2, 5, 2) =
2581  (psi2(2, 5, 0) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 5, 3) * dxids0[1] +
2582  psi2(2, 5, 4) * dxids0[2]) *
2583  dxids1[0] +
2584  (psi2(2, 5, 3) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 5, 1) * dxids0[1] +
2585  psi2(2, 5, 5) * dxids0[2]) *
2586  dxids1[1] +
2587  (psi2(2, 5, 4) * dxids0[0] + psi2(2, 5, 5) * dxids0[1] +
2588  psi2(2, 5, 2) * dxids0[2]) *
2589  dxids1[2];
2590  }
2591  };
2592 
2593  ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
2594  ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
2595  // C1CurvedElementsShape
2596  ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
2597  ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
2598  //========================================================================
2599  /// A class for Linear triangular shape function with 3 vertex nodes
2600  //========================================================================
2601  template<unsigned DIM>
2602  class LinearTElement
2603  {
2604  };
2605 
2606  template<>
2607  class LinearTElement<2>
2608  {
2609  public:
2610  //=======================================================================
2611  /// Return local coordinates of node j
2612  //=======================================================================
2613  void local_coordinate_of_node(const unsigned& j, Vector<double>& s) const
2614  {
2615  switch (j)
2616  {
2617  case 0:
2618  s[0] = 1.0;
2619  s[1] = 0.0;
2620  break;
2621 
2622  case 1:
2623  s[0] = 0.0;
2624  s[1] = 1.0;
2625  break;
2626 
2627  case 2:
2628  s[0] = 0.0;
2629  s[1] = 0.0;
2630  break;
2631 
2632  default:
2633  std::ostringstream error_message;
2634  error_message
2635  << "Element only has three nodes; called with node number " << j
2636  << std::endl;
2637 
2638  throw OomphLibError(error_message.str(),
2639  "TElement::local_coordinate_of_node()",
2640  OOMPH_EXCEPTION_LOCATION);
2641  }
2642  }
2643 
2644 
2645  //=======================================================================
2646  /// Shape function for specific TElement<2,2>
2647  //=======================================================================
2648  void Lshape(const Vector<double>& s, Shape& psi) const
2649  {
2650  psi[0] = s[0];
2651  psi[1] = s[1];
2652  psi[2] = 1.0 - s[0] - s[1];
2653  }
2654 
2655 
2656  //=======================================================================
2657  /// Derivatives of shape functions for specific TElement<2,2>
2658  //=======================================================================
2659  void dLshape_local(const Vector<double>& s,
2660  Shape& psi,
2661  DShape& dpsids) const
2662  {
2663  this->Lshape(s, psi);
2664 
2665  // Derivatives
2666  dpsids(0, 0) = 1.0;
2667  dpsids(0, 1) = 0.0;
2668  dpsids(1, 0) = 0.0;
2669  dpsids(1, 1) = 1.0;
2670  dpsids(2, 0) = -1.0;
2671  dpsids(2, 1) = -1.0;
2672  }
2673 
2674 
2675  //=======================================================================
2676  /// Second derivatives of shape functions for specific TElement<2,2>:
2677  /// d2psids(i,0) = \f$ \partial^2 \psi_j / \partial s_0^2 \f$ \n
2678  /// d2psids(i,1) = \f$ \partial^2 \psi_j / \partial s_1^2 \f$ \n
2679  /// d2psids(i,2) = \f$ \partial^2 \psi_j / \partial s_0 \partial s_1 \f$ \n
2680  //=======================================================================
2681  void d2Lshape_local(const Vector<double>& s,
2682  Shape& psi,
2683  DShape& dpsids,
2684  DShape& d2psids) const
2685  {
2686  this->dLshape_local(s, psi, dpsids);
2687 
2688  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 3; i++)
2689  {
2690  d2psids(i, 0) = 0.0;
2691  d2psids(i, 1) = 0.0;
2692  d2psids(i, 2) = 0.0;
2693  }
2694  }
2695  };

2697  //=====================================================================
2698  /// Define integration schemes that are required to exactly integrate
2699  /// the mass matrices of the bubble-enriched elements. The enrichement
2700  /// increases the polynomial order which means that higher-order Gauss
2701  /// rules must be used.
2702  //====================================================================
2703  template<unsigned DIM, unsigned NNODE_1D>
2704  class CurvedTGauss
2705  {
2706  };
2707 
2708  //====================================================================
2709  /// Specialisation for two-dimensional elements, in which the highest
2710  /// order polynomial is cubic, so we need the integration scheme
2711  /// for the unenriched cubic element
2712  //======================================================================
2713  template<>
2714  class CurvedTGauss<2, 2> : public TGauss<2, 4>
2715  {
2716  public:
2717  CurvedTGauss() : TGauss<2, 4>() {}
2718  };

2720  //========================================================================
2721  /// A class for subparametric shape functions of
2722  /// a curved triangular element with 3 vertex nodes
2723  /// Affine mapping is used when dealing with a straight-boundary element
2724  /// Nonlinear mapping is used when dealing with a curved-boundary element
2725  /// Note that a cubic-Hermite polynomial is employed to approximate a
2726  /// curved boundary
2727  //========================================================================
2728  template<unsigned DIM>
2729  class GeometricTElement
2730  {
2731  };
2732 
2733  template<>
2734  class GeometricTElement<2>
2735  {
2736  public:
2737  //=======================================================================
2738  /// Return local coordinates of node j
2739  //=======================================================================
2740  void local_coordinate_of_node(const unsigned& j, Vector<double>& s) const
2741  {
2742  switch (j)
2743  {
2744  case 0:
2745  s[0] = 1.0;
2746  s[1] = 0.0;
2747  break;
2748 
2749  case 1:
2750  s[0] = 0.0;
2751  s[1] = 1.0;
2752  break;
2753 
2754  case 2:
2755  s[0] = 0.0;
2756  s[1] = 0.0;
2757  break;
2758 
2759  default:
2760  std::ostringstream error_message;
2761  error_message
2762  << "Element only has three nodes; called with node number " << j
2763  << std::endl;
2764 
2765  throw OomphLibError(error_message.str(),
2766  "GeometricTElement::local_coordinate_of_node()",
2767  OOMPH_EXCEPTION_LOCATION);
2768  }
2769  }
2770  //=======================================================================
2771  /// Geometric interpolation for specific C1CurvedElement<>
2772  /// This function return the physical coordinates at the local coordinate s
2773  /// rather than a value of shape function at the local coordinate s
2774  //=======================================================================
2775  void Lshape(const Vector<double>& s,
2776  Shape& psi,
2777  Shape& phi,
2778  DenseMatrix<double>& position,
2779  unsigned& bd_element,
2780  DenseMatrix<double>& bd_position,
2781  Vector<double>& x) const
2782  {
2783  // assign shape functions to the interior elements
2784  psi[0] = s[0];
2785  psi[1] = s[1];
2786  psi[2] = 1.0 - s[0] - s[1];
2787 
2788  // assign shape functions to the boundary elements
2789  double angle_1 = atan2(bd_position(0, 1), bd_position(0, 0));
2790  double angle_2 = atan2(bd_position(1, 1), bd_position(1, 0));
2791  double angle_min = 0.0;
2792  double angle_max = 0.0;
2793 
2794  DenseMatrix<double> p(3, 2);
2795  if (angle_1 < angle_2)
2796  {
2797  angle_min = angle_1;
2798  angle_max = angle_2;
2799 
2800  p(0, 0) = bd_position(0, 0);
2801  p(0, 1) = bd_position(0, 1);
2802 
2803  p(1, 0) = bd_position(1, 0);
2804  p(1, 1) = bd_position(1, 1);
2805  }
2806  else if (angle_1 > angle_2)
2807  {
2808  angle_min = angle_2;
2809  angle_max = angle_1;
2810 
2811  p(0, 0) = bd_position(1, 0);
2812  p(0, 1) = bd_position(1, 1);
2813 
2814  p(1, 0) = bd_position(0, 0);
2815  p(1, 1) = bd_position(0, 1);
2816  }
2817 
2818  Vector<double> b_fn_derivative_min(2), b_fn_derivative_max(2);
2819  b_fn_derivative_min[0] = -1.0 * sin(angle_min);
2820  b_fn_derivative_min[1] = cos(angle_min);
2821  b_fn_derivative_max[0] = -1.0 * sin(angle_max);
2822  b_fn_derivative_max[1] = cos(angle_max);
2823 
2824  // compute the physical coordinates at the local coordinate s
2825  if (bd_element == 0)
2826  {
2827  phi[0] = position(2, 0) + (position(0, 0) - position(2, 0)) * s[0] +
2828  (position(1, 0) - position(2, 0)) * s[1];
2829  phi[1] = position(2, 1) + (position(0, 1) - position(2, 1)) * s[0] +
2830  (position(1, 1) - position(2, 1)) * s[1];
2831  }
2832  else
2833  {
2834  Vector<double> psi_h(2);
2835  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
2836  {
2837  // polynomial of degree 3 to approximate boundary
2838  psi_h[i] = ((2.0 * (p(1, i) - p(0, i)) -
2839  (angle_max - angle_min) *
2840  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] + b_fn_derivative_max[i])) *
2841  (s[1] - s[0]) +
2842  (angle_max - angle_min) *
2843  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] - b_fn_derivative_max[i]));
2844  phi[i] = x[i] + (p(0, i) - x[i]) * s[0] + (p(1, i) - x[i]) * s[1] +
2845  1.0 / 2.0 * s[0] * s[1] * psi_h[i];
2846  }
2847  }
2848  }
2849 
2850 
2851  //=======================================================================
2852  /// Derivatives of Geometric interpolation for specific C1CurvedElement<>
2853  /// This function return the derivatives of physical coordinates at
2854  /// the local coordinate s rather than a value of the derivatives of
2855  /// shape function at the local coordinate s
2856  //=======================================================================
2857  void dLshape_local(const Vector<double>& s,
2858  Shape& psi,
2859  DShape& dpsids,
2860  Shape& phi,
2861  DShape& dphids,
2862  DenseMatrix<double>& position,
2863  unsigned& bd_element,
2864  DenseMatrix<double>& bd_position,
2865  Vector<double>& x) const
2866  {
2867  this->Lshape(s, psi, phi, position, bd_element, bd_position, x);
2868  // Derivatives
2869  dpsids(0, 0) = 1.0;
2870  dpsids(0, 1) = 0.0;
2871  dpsids(1, 0) = 0.0;
2872  dpsids(1, 1) = 1.0;
2873  dpsids(2, 0) = -1.0;
2874  dpsids(2, 1) = -1.0;
2875 
2876  double angle_1 = atan2(bd_position(0, 1), bd_position(0, 0));
2877  double angle_2 = atan2(bd_position(1, 1), bd_position(1, 0));
2878  double angle_min = 0.0;
2879  double angle_max = 0.0;
2880 
2881  DenseMatrix<double> p(3, 2);
2882  if (angle_1 < angle_2)
2883  {
2884  angle_min = angle_1;
2885  angle_max = angle_2;
2886 
2887  p(0, 0) = bd_position(0, 0);
2888  p(0, 1) = bd_position(0, 1);
2889 
2890  p(1, 0) = bd_position(1, 0);
2891  p(1, 1) = bd_position(1, 1);
2892  }
2893  else if (angle_1 > angle_2)
2894  {
2895  angle_min = angle_2;
2896  angle_max = angle_1;
2897 
2898  p(0, 0) = bd_position(1, 0);
2899  p(0, 1) = bd_position(1, 1);
2900 
2901  p(1, 0) = bd_position(0, 0);
2902  p(1, 1) = bd_position(0, 1);
2903  }
2904 
2905  Vector<double> b_fn_derivative_min(2), b_fn_derivative_max(2);
2906  b_fn_derivative_min[0] = -1.0 * sin(angle_min);
2907  b_fn_derivative_min[1] = cos(angle_min);
2908  b_fn_derivative_max[0] = -1.0 * sin(angle_max);
2909  b_fn_derivative_max[1] = cos(angle_max);
2910 
2911  // compute shape functions
2912  if (bd_element == 0)
2913  {
2914  dphids(0, 0) = position(0, 0) - position(2, 0);
2915  dphids(0, 1) = position(1, 0) - position(2, 0);
2916  dphids(1, 0) = position(0, 1) - position(2, 1);
2917  dphids(1, 1) = position(1, 1) - position(2, 1);
2918  }
2919  else
2920  {
2921  Vector<double> psi_h(2);
2922  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
2923  {
2924  psi_h[i] = ((2.0 * (p(1, i) - p(0, i)) -
2925  (angle_max - angle_min) *
2926  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] + b_fn_derivative_max[i])) *
2927  (s[1] - s[0]) +
2928  (angle_max - angle_min) *
2929  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] - b_fn_derivative_max[i]));
2930  }
2931  // compute shape functions derivatives
2932  DenseMatrix<double> dpsi_h(2, 2);
2933  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
2934  {
2935  dpsi_h(i, 0) = (2.0 * (p(1, i) - p(0, i)) -
2936  (angle_max - angle_min) *
2937  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] + b_fn_derivative_max[i])) *
2938  (-1.0);
2939  dpsi_h(i, 1) = (2.0 * (p(1, i) - p(0, i)) -
2940  (angle_max - angle_min) *
2941  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] + b_fn_derivative_max[i]));
2942  }
2943  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
2944  {
2945  dphids(i, 0) = p(0, i) - x[i] +
2946  1.0 / 2.0 * s[0] * s[1] * dpsi_h(i, 0) +
2947  psi_h[i] * s[1] / 2.0;
2948  dphids(i, 1) = p(1, i) - x[i] +
2949  1.0 / 2.0 * s[0] * s[1] * dpsi_h(i, 1) +
2950  psi_h[i] * s[0] / 2.0;
2951  }
2952  }
2953  }
2954 
2955  //=======================================================================
2956  /// Second derivatives of Geometric interpolation for
2957  /// specific C1CurvedElement<>:
2958  /// This function return the second-order derivatives of physical
2959  /// coordinates at the local coordinate s rather than a value of the
2960  /// second-order derivatives of shape function at the local coordinate s
2961  ///=======================================================================
2962  void d2Lshape_local(const Vector<double>& s,
2963  Shape& psi,
2964  DShape& dpsids,
2965  DShape& d2psids,
2966  Shape& phi,
2967  DShape& dphids,
2968  DShape& d2phids,
2969  DenseMatrix<double>& position,
2970  unsigned& bd_element,
2971  DenseMatrix<double>& bd_position,
2972  Vector<double>& x) const
2973  {
2974  this->dLshape_local(
2975  s, psi, dpsids, phi, dphids, position, bd_element, bd_position, x);
2976  // 2nd Derivatives
2977  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 3; i++)
2978  {
2979  d2psids(i, 0) = 0.0;
2980  d2psids(i, 1) = 0.0;
2981  d2psids(i, 2) = 0.0;
2982  }
2983  double angle_1 = atan2(bd_position(0, 1), bd_position(0, 0));
2984  double angle_2 = atan2(bd_position(1, 1), bd_position(1, 0));
2985  double angle_min = 0.0;
2986  double angle_max = 0.0;
2987 
2988  DenseMatrix<double> p(3, 2);
2989  if (angle_1 < angle_2)
2990  {
2991  angle_min = angle_1;
2992  angle_max = angle_2;
2993 
2994  p(0, 0) = bd_position(0, 0);
2995  p(0, 1) = bd_position(0, 1);
2996 
2997  p(1, 0) = bd_position(1, 0);
2998  p(1, 1) = bd_position(1, 1);
2999  }
3000  else if (angle_1 > angle_2)
3001  {
3002  angle_min = angle_2;
3003  angle_max = angle_1;
3004 
3005  p(0, 0) = bd_position(1, 0);
3006  p(0, 1) = bd_position(1, 1);
3007 
3008  p(1, 0) = bd_position(0, 0);
3009  p(1, 1) = bd_position(0, 1);
3010  }
3011 
3012  Vector<double> b_fn_derivative_min(2), b_fn_derivative_max(2);
3013  b_fn_derivative_min[0] = -1.0 * sin(angle_min);
3014  b_fn_derivative_min[1] = cos(angle_min);
3015  b_fn_derivative_max[0] = -1.0 * sin(angle_max);
3016  b_fn_derivative_max[1] = cos(angle_max);
3017 
3018  // compute the 2nd-order of derivatives of the physical coordinates
3019  if (bd_element == 0)
3020  {
3021  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
3022  {
3023  d2phids(i, 0) = 0.0;
3024  d2phids(i, 1) = 0.0;
3025  d2phids(i, 2) = 0.0;
3026  }
3027  }
3028  else
3029  {
3030  // compute the 2nd-order derivatives of the physical coordinates
3031  Vector<double> psi_h(2);
3032  DenseMatrix<double> dpsi_h(2, 2), d2psi_h(2, 3);
3033 
3034  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
3035  {
3036  psi_h[i] = ((2.0 * (p(1, i) - p(0, i)) -
3037  (angle_max - angle_min) *
3038  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] + b_fn_derivative_max[i])) *
3039  (s[1] - s[0]) +
3040  (angle_max - angle_min) *
3041  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] - b_fn_derivative_max[i]));
3042  }
3043 
3044  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
3045  {
3046  dpsi_h(i, 0) = (2.0 * (p(1, i) - p(0, i)) -
3047  (angle_max - angle_min) *
3048  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] + b_fn_derivative_max[i])) *
3049  (-1.0);
3050  dpsi_h(i, 1) = (2.0 * (p(1, i) - p(0, i)) -
3051  (angle_max - angle_min) *
3052  (b_fn_derivative_min[i] + b_fn_derivative_max[i]));
3053  }
3054 
3055  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
3056  {
3057  d2psi_h(i, 0) = 0.0;
3058  d2psi_h(i, 1) = 0.0;
3059  d2psi_h(i, 2) = 0.0;
3060  }
3061 
3062  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
3063  {
3064  d2phids(i, 0) = 1.0 / 2.0 * s[0] * s[1] * d2psi_h(i, 0) +
3065  dpsi_h(i, 0) * s[1] / 2.0 +
3066  1.0 / 2.0 * s[1] * dpsi_h(i, 0);
3067  d2phids(i, 1) = 1.0 / 2.0 * s[0] * s[1] * d2psi_h(i, 1) +
3068  1.0 / 2.0 * s[0] * dpsi_h(i, 1) +
3069  1.0 / 2.0 * s[0] * dpsi_h(i, 1);
3070  d2phids(i, 2) = 1.0 / 2.0 * s[0] * s[1] * d2psi_h(i, 2) +
3071  1.0 / 2.0 * s[0] * dpsi_h(i, 0) + psi_h[i] / 2.0 +
3072  dpsi_h(i, 1) * s[1] / 2.0;
3073  }
3074  }
3075  }
3076  };
3077

3204  ///============================================================
3205  /// compute for the set of value in the reference triangle
3206  ///============================================================
3207  void set_of_value(DenseMatrix<double>& D,
3208  DenseMatrix<double>& B,
3209  DenseMatrix<double>& position,
3210  unsigned& bd_element,
3211  DenseMatrix<double>& bd_position,
3212  Vector<double>& x) const
3213  {
3214  double angle_1 = atan2(bd_position(0, 1), bd_position(0, 0));
3215  double angle_2 = atan2(bd_position(1, 1), bd_position(1, 0));
3216  double angle_min = 0.0;
3217  double angle_max = 0.0;
3218 
3219  DenseMatrix<double> p(3, 2);
3220  if (angle_1 < angle_2)
3221  {
3222  angle_min = angle_1;
3223  angle_max = angle_2;
3224 
3225  p(0, 0) = bd_position(0, 0);
3226  p(0, 1) = bd_position(0, 1);
3227 
3228  p(1, 0) = bd_position(1, 0);
3229  p(1, 1) = bd_position(1, 1);
3230  }
3231  else if (angle_1 > angle_2)
3232  {
3233  angle_min = angle_2;
3234  angle_max = angle_1;
3235 
3236  p(0, 0) = bd_position(1, 0);
3237  p(0, 1) = bd_position(1, 1);
3238 
3239  p(1, 0) = bd_position(0, 0);
3240  p(1, 1) = bd_position(0, 1);
3241  }
3242  p(2, 0) = x[0];
3243  p(2, 1) = x[1];
3244 
3245  Vector<double> fn_derivative1(2), fn_derivative2(2);
3246  fn_derivative1[0] = (angle_max - angle_min) * -1.0 * sin(angle_min);
3247  fn_derivative1[1] = (angle_max - angle_min) * -1.0 * sin(angle_max);
3248  fn_derivative2[0] = (angle_max - angle_min) * cos(angle_min);
3249  fn_derivative2[1] = (angle_max - angle_min) * cos(angle_max);
3250 
3251  // compute for the transformation matrix D from global to local
3252  // coordinates
3253  // initialise the matrix first
3254  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 21; i++)
3255  {
3256  for (unsigned j = 0; j < 21; j++)
3257  {
3258  D(i, j) = 0.0;
3259  }
3260  }
3261  double x31, x23, x13, x32, y13, y31, y32, y23;
3262  x31 = p(2, 0) - p(0, 0);
3263  y31 = p(2, 1) - p(0, 1);
3264  x32 = p(2, 0) - p(1, 0);
3265  y32 = p(2, 1) - p(1, 1);
3266  x23 = p(1, 0) - p(2, 0);
3267  y23 = p(1, 1) - p(2, 1);
3268  x13 = p(0, 0) - p(2, 0);
3269  y13 = p(0, 1) - p(2, 1);
3270 
3271  // assign values to the matrix D
3272  D(0, 0) = 1.0;
3273  D(1, 1) = 1.0;
3274  D(2, 2) = 1.0;
3275  D(3 + 0, 3 + 0) = x31;
3276  D(3 + 0, 3 + 1) = fn_derivative1[0];
3277  D(3 + 1, 3 + 0) = y31;
3278  D(3 + 1, 3 + 1) = fn_derivative2[0];
3279  // define submatrix d2
3280  D(5 + 0, 5 + 0) = -1.0 * fn_derivative1[1];
3281  D(5 + 0, 5 + 1) = x32;
3282  D(5 + 1, 5 + 0) = -1.0 * fn_derivative2[1];
3283  D(5 + 1, 5 + 1) = y32;
3284  // define submatrix d3
3285  D(7 + 0, 7 + 0) = x23;
3286  D(7 + 0, 7 + 1) = x13;
3287  D(7 + 1, 7 + 0) = y23;
3288  D(7 + 1, 7 + 1) = y13;
3289  // define submatrix d4
3290  D(9 + 0, 9 + 0) = x31 * x31;
3291  D(9 + 0, 9 + 1) = fn_derivative1[0] * fn_derivative1[0];
3292  D(9 + 0, 9 + 6) = x32 * x32;
3293  D(9 + 1, 9 + 0) = 2.0 * x31 * y31;
3294  D(9 + 1, 9 + 1) = 2.0 * fn_derivative1[0] * fn_derivative2[0];
3295  D(9 + 1, 9 + 6) = 2.0 * x32 * y32;
3296  D(9 + 2, 9 + 0) = y31 * y31;
3297  D(9 + 2, 9 + 1) = fn_derivative2[0] * fn_derivative2[0];
3298  D(9 + 2, 9 + 6) = y32 * y32;
3299  D(9 + 3, 9 + 2) = fn_derivative1[1] * fn_derivative1[1];
3300  D(9 + 3, 9 + 3) = x32 * x32;
3301  D(9 + 3, 9 + 7) = x31 * x31;
3302  D(9 + 4, 9 + 2) = 2.0 * fn_derivative1[1] * fn_derivative2[1];
3303  D(9 + 4, 9 + 3) = 2.0 * x32 * y32;
3304  D(9 + 4, 9 + 7) = 2.0 * x31 * y31;
3305  D(9 + 5, 9 + 2) = fn_derivative2[1] * fn_derivative2[1];
3306  D(9 + 5, 9 + 3) = y32 * y32;
3307  D(9 + 5, 9 + 7) = y31 * y31;
3308  D(9 + 6, 9 + 4) = x32 * x32;
3309  D(9 + 6, 9 + 5) = x31 * x31;
3310  D(9 + 6, 9 + 8) = fn_derivative1[0] * fn_derivative1[1];
3311  D(9 + 7, 9 + 4) = 2.0 * x32 * y32;
3312  D(9 + 7, 9 + 5) = 2.0 * x31 * y31;
3313  D(9 + 7, 9 + 8) = fn_derivative1[0] * fn_derivative2[1] +
3314  fn_derivative2[0] * fn_derivative1[1];
3315  D(9 + 8, 9 + 4) = y32 * y32;
3316  D(9 + 8, 9 + 5) = y31 * y31;
3317  D(9 + 8, 9 + 8) = fn_derivative2[0] * fn_derivative2[1];
3318 
3319  D(18, 18) = 1.0;
3320  D(19, 19) = 1.0;
3321  D(20, 20) = 1.0;
3322  // assign the matrix of transformation from the dofs on curved element to
3323  // the dofs on reference element
3324  DenseMatrix<double> Bt(36, 21);
3325  // Initialize the matrix
3326  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 36; i++)
3327  {
3328  for (unsigned j = 0; j < 21; j++)
3329  {
3330  Bt(i, j) = 0.0;
3331  }
3332  }
3333  // submatrix b1
3334  Bt(0, 0) = 1.0;
3335  Bt(1, 1) = 1.0;
3336  Bt(2, 2) = 1.0;
3337  // submatrix b2
3338  Bt(3 + 0, 3 + 0) = -1.0;
3339  Bt(3 + 1, 3 + 0) = -1.0;
3340  Bt(3 + 1, 3 + 1) = 1.0;
3341  Bt(3 + 2, 3 + 2) = 1.0;
3342  Bt(3 + 2, 3 + 3) = -1.0;
3343  Bt(3 + 3, 3 + 3) = -1.0;
3344  Bt(3 + 4, 3 + 5) = 1.0;
3345  Bt(3 + 5, 3 + 4) = 1.0;
3346  // submatrix b3
3347  double a1, a2, aa1, aa2, b1, b2, bb1, bb2, c1, c2, cc1, cc2;
3348  Vector<double> A1(2), A2(2), B1(2), B2(2), C1(2), C2(2);
3349  for (unsigned i = 0; i < 2; i++)
3350  {
3351  A1[i] = p(2, i) - p(0, i);
3352  B2[i] = p(2, i) - p(1, i);
3353  C1[i] = p(1, i) - p(2, i);
3354  C2[i] = p(0, i) - p(2, i);
3355  }
3356  A2[0] = (angle_max - angle_min) * -1.0 * sin(angle_min);
3357  A2[1] = (angle_max - angle_min) * cos(angle_min);
3358  B1[0] = -1.0 * (angle_max - angle_min) * -1.0 * sin(angle_max);
3359  B1[1] = -1.0 * (angle_max - angle_min) * cos(angle_max);
3360  double B2xA2, A1xA2, A1xB2, B1xA2, A1xB1, B1xA1, A2xB2, B1xB2;
3361  B2xA2 = B2[0] * A2[1] - B2[1] * A2[0];
3362  A1xA2 = A1[0] * A2[1] - A1[1] * A2[0];
3363  A1xB2 = A1[0] * B2[1] - A1[1] * B2[0];
3364  B1xA2 = B1[0] * A2[1] - B1[1] * A2[0];
3365  A1xB1 = A1[0] * B1[1] - A1[1] * B1[0];
3366  A2xB2 = A2[0] * B2[1] - A2[1] * B2[0];
3367  B1xA1 = B1[0] * A1[1] - B1[1] * A1[0];
3368  B1xB2 = B1[0] * B2[1] - B1[1] * B2[0];
3369  a1 = B2xA2 / A1xA2 - 1.0;
3370  a2 = A1xB2 / A1xA2;
3371  aa1 = -1.0 * B1xA2 / A1xA2;
3372  aa2 = -1.0 * A1xB1 / A1xA2;
3373  b1 = A1xB2 / B1xB2;
3374  b2 = B1xA1 / B1xB2 - 1.0;
3375  bb1 = A2xB2 / B1xB2;
3376  bb2 = B1xA2 / B1xB2;
3377  c1 = -1.0 / a2;
3378  c2 = -1.0 * bb1 / b1;
3379  cc1 = aa2 / a2;
3380  cc2 = -1.0 / b1;
3381 
3382  Bt(9 + 1, 3 + 0) = 2.0 * a1 + aa1 / 2.0;
3383  Bt(9 + 2, 3 + 0) = -1.0 * (2.0 * a1 + aa1);
3384  Bt(9 + 1, 3 + 1) = 3.0 / 2.0 + 2.0 * a2 + aa2 / 2.0;
3385  Bt(9 + 2, 3 + 1) = -1.0 * (1.0 + 2.0 * a2 + aa2);
3386  Bt(9 + 3, 3 + 2) = -1.0 * (1.0 + 2.0 * b1 - bb1);
3387  Bt(9 + 4, 3 + 2) = 3.0 / 2.0 + 2.0 * b1 - bb1 / 2.0;
3388  Bt(9 + 3, 3 + 3) = -1.0 * (2.0 * b2 - bb2);
3389  Bt(9 + 4, 3 + 3) = 2.0 * b2 - bb2 / 2.0;
3390  Bt(9 + 7, 3 + 4) = (c1 + cc1) / 2.0;
3391  Bt(9 + 7, 3 + 5) = (c2 + cc2) / 2.0;
3392 
3393  Bt(9 + 0, 9 + 0) = 1.0;
3394  Bt(9 + 1, 9 + 0) = 1.0 + (1.0 + a1) / (2.0 * a2);
3395  Bt(9 + 2, 9 + 0) = 1.0 + (1.0 + a1) / (a2);
3396  Bt(9 + 1, 9 + 1) = (a2) / (2.0 * (1.0 + a1));
3397  Bt(9 + 2, 9 + 1) = 1.0 + (a2) / (1.0 + a1);
3398  Bt(9 + 3, 9 + 2) = 1.0 + (b1) / (1.0 + b2);
3399  Bt(9 + 4, 9 + 2) = (b1) / (2.0 * (1.0 + b2));
3400  Bt(9 + 3, 9 + 3) = 1.0 + (1.0 + b2) / (b1);
3401  Bt(9 + 4, 9 + 3) = 1.0 + (1.0 + b2) / (2.0 * b1);
3402  Bt(9 + 5, 9 + 3) = 1.0;
3403  Bt(9 + 7, 9 + 4) = -1.0 * (c1 * cc1) / (c1 * cc2 + c2 * cc1);
3404  Bt(9 + 8, 9 + 4) = 1.0;
3405  Bt(9 + 6, 9 + 5) = 1.0;
3406  Bt(9 + 7, 9 + 5) = -1.0 * (c2 * cc2) / (c1 * cc2 + c2 * cc1);
3407  Bt(9 + 1, 9 + 6) = (-1.0) / (2.0 * a2 * (1.0 + a1));
3408  Bt(9 + 2, 9 + 6) = (-1.0) / (a2 * (1.0 + a1));
3409  Bt(9 + 3, 9 + 7) = (-1.0) / (b1 * (1.0 + b2));
3410  Bt(9 + 4, 9 + 7) = (-1.0) / (2.0 * b1 * (1.0 + b2));
3411  Bt(9 + 7, 9 + 8) = (-1.0) / (c1 * cc2 + c2 * cc1);
3412 
3413  double ata1, ata2;
3414  // assign the points of perpendicular for the sides a1a3 nd a2a3
3415  Vector<double> s1(2), s2(2);
3416  // find the point that the point a1(on the boundary) is perpendicular to
3417  // the vector a2a3
3418  double m = (p(1, 1) - p(2, 1)) / (p(1, 0) - p(2, 0));
3419  double k = p(2, 1) - m * p(2, 0);
3420  s1[0] =
3421  ((p(1, 0) - p(2, 0)) * p(0, 0) + (p(1, 1) - p(2, 1)) * (p(0, 1) - k)) /
3422  ((p(1, 0) - p(2, 0)) + (p(1, 1) - p(2, 1)) * m);
3423  s1[1] = m * s1[0] + k;
3424 
3425  if ((p(1, 0) - p(2, 0)) == 0)
3426  {
3427  m = (p(1, 0) - p(2, 0)) / (p(1, 1) - p(2, 1));
3428  k = p(2, 0) - m * p(2, 1);
3429  s1[1] = ((p(1, 0) - p(2, 0)) * (p(0, 0) - k) +
3430  (p(1, 1) - p(2, 1)) * (p(0, 1))) /
3431  ((p(1, 0) - p(2, 0)) * m + (p(1, 1) - p(2, 1)));
3432  s1[0] = m * s1[1] + k;
3433  }
3434 
3435  // find the point that the point a2(on the boundary) is perpendicular to
3436  // the vector a1a3
3437  m = (p(0, 1) - p(2, 1)) / (p(0, 0) - p(2, 0));
3438  k = p(2, 1) - m * p(2, 0);
3439  s2[0] =
3440  ((p(0, 0) - p(2, 0)) * p(1, 0) + (p(0, 1) - p(2, 1)) * (p(1, 1) - k)) /
3441  ((p(0, 0) - p(2, 0)) + (p(0, 1) - p(2, 1)) * m);
3442  s2[1] = m * s2[0] + k;
3443 
3444  if ((p(0, 0) - p(2, 0)) == 0)
3445  {
3446  m = (p(0, 0) - p(2, 0)) / (p(0, 1) - p(2, 1));
3447  k = p(2, 0) - m * p(2, 1);
